I was walking around

533
00:21:51,875 --> 00:21:53,583
and setting up
equipment with Yasu.

534
00:21:56,083 --> 00:21:57,000
Who's that?

535
00:22:04,041 --> 00:22:06,041
That's the school...

536
00:22:06,125 --> 00:22:08,666
Wait, that means
I'm on the roof.

537
00:22:18,875 --> 00:22:21,041
Are... those souls?

538
00:22:21,875 --> 00:22:23,208
Hey.

539
00:22:23,291 --> 00:22:25,416
Do you know what all
those little lights are?

540
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,375
Of course I do.

541
00:22:27,458 --> 00:22:29,166
That's why it's so fun.

542
00:22:29,916 --> 00:22:31,291
It's so fun?

543
00:22:34,875 --> 00:22:36,791
So much... fun...

544
00:22:36,875 --> 00:22:38,500
There is nothing
in the whole world

545
00:22:38,583 --> 00:22:40,291
that feels better than this.

546
00:22:40,375 --> 00:22:41,875
It's you.

547
00:22:41,958 --> 00:22:43,541
He was a freshman
that went here...

548
00:22:43,625 --> 00:22:45,291
Committed suicide.

549
00:22:45,375 --> 00:22:47,166
Sakauchi...

550
00:22:47,250 --> 00:22:49,083
you know the kid who
committed suicide...

